From Robert Martin 2001-01-15 19:02:34<br/>
<br/>
If you ever have a couple of hours to kill on a Sunday afternoon on your way home, check out<br/>
Sandstone Falls. It is awesome. They have a nice park there with a boardwalk that will give you<br/>
access to the many veiwing points. It could be run (sneaked) on the far far left. The center of the<br/>
falls is a good 20'+ vertical drop and the right line is a class VI monster. &quot;It's not for<br/>
runnin', it's just for lookin at.&quot; </div>
